CM_ SG_ 601 Pack2_NegMCFlt "If fail to close negative main contactor.";
CM_ SG_ 601 Pack2_CPUFlt "CPU fault occured on BECM 2 (unexpected reset, watchdog timeout, NVM error, I/O fault).";
